Domain:  Mathematics
Topic:   Euler's Identity
Formula: e^(iπ) + 1 = 0
Note:    Relates five fundamental constants; called most beautiful equation

Domain:  Medicine
Topic:   Blood Types
Formula: ABO system + Rh factor
Note:    Determines blood transfusion compatibility

Domain:  Biology
Topic:   Cell Theory
Formula: All life is made of cells arising from pre-existing cells
Note:    Foundation of modern biology

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   1st Law of Thermodynamics
Formula: ΔU = Q - W
Note:    Energy conservation in thermodynamic systems

Domain:  Chemistry
Topic:   pH Definition
Formula: pH = -log[H+]
Note:    Measure of hydrogen ion concentration; 7 is neutral

